KERN Place.  Approx. 2800 square feet, including basement apartment with bedroom, fireplace, and kitchenette. New tile, hardwood, granite counter tops. Large pool and large two car garage.

One of the finest old neighborhoods in El Paso. Close to hospitals, Mesita school, shopping, restaurant, Downtown and UTEP.
